<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=5804&amp;p=154398#p154398"><![CDATA[
Another possible issue is the game writes to the Program Bank register at $2FFF which is valid, but the Smart Card doesn't like this. I would assume this is causing the crash. <br /><br />So it's your lucky day I guess. I patched the ones that I saw and you can give this patch a try. Tell us if it works for you.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=1726">MottZilla</a> — Mon Aug 31, 2015 12:28 pm</p><hr />
